Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,君主们堕落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们终日战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.67,0:00:12.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不愿听神明的教诲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.93,0:00:15.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非但如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.51,0:00:18.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,僭称皇帝的提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,独占了唯一神的碎片——圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.31,0:00:25.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欲将大陆据为己有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.61,0:00:31.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我身为神的代理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.19,0:00:36.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在此宣布发起圣战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.41,0:02:26.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到圣印教团居然会在这时候与我们为敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣印教团在想什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为么要妨碍我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.67,0:02:37.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为圣印教团和魔法师协会勾结了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有根据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.76,0:02:43.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会肃清君主派魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.72,0:02:46.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,选择与君主对决是在昨晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  就在第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,教团宣布对皇帝军发动圣战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.81,0:02:55.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且布阵还挡住了前往埃兰姆的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要说是偶然就巧过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇的军队有多少人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.87,0:03:06.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣战士有两干  佣兵团三千左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过信徒数量有八万以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:15.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过其中包含着大量老人和小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣战士和佣兵还好说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟无辜的人们战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解提欧大人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.01,0:03:30.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟提欧大人至今一直在为民众战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你无法战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就由我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不会变成战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为唯一神不希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.16,0:03:42.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去见雷欧涅大人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我来说服他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:53.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.46,0:03:59.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇已做出宣言 你是假的  自己才是圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是去找这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能会被杀掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我也非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:09.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为这才是我该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要听她的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连你也这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然教团已逼教徒上战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人就不能跟教团战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是继续让他们挡道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.74,0:04:28.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇军早晚也会拿信徒当盾牌攻打过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我军很可能全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  都无计可施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.54,0:04:38.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  绝不能让她只身奔赴险境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.05,0:04:39.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我也要随行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝军有何动向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上布阵  没有准备行动的迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.86,0:05:01.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必是被唯一神和教皇震慑住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就提欧・科尔内罗那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.78,0:05:09.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要不了多久便会跪在教皇面前乞求原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,信徒们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很愿意聚集起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:18.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  看起来对于与英雄提欧•科尔内罗开战一事也有犹豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,士气绝算不上高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.21,0:05:25.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟圣女普莉希拉正侍奉皇帝的消息已经传开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟圣女派的人认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.26,0:05:32.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗会将皇帝圣印献给圣女普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一神将就此复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说我军数量更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  皇帝军的训练度和装备更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.95,0:05:49.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  想赢皇帝军恐怕很难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗  没必要赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,或许反倒应该大败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.00,0:06:03.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦君主们虐杀了教团信徒的消息传开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必提欧•科尔内罗的名声会一落干丈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,云达团长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请开始准备向皇帝军发动攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上  全面派出信徒发动攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣战士团和佣兵团就留在阵中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人竟然亲自前来送行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会说服教皇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请静候佳音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能平安回来就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这么打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那扫帚是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我找白魔女长老学了制作方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然用起来没魔杖顺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过即值如此  只要有它就能提高注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文  艾雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她俩就交给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.56,0:07:06.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,必须报救了我两命的恩才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,相信她俩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我等此行是有事想请求雷欧涅猊下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.95,0:07:58.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言 提欧皇帝不希望与猊下战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝军的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是平定埃兰姆的骚乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过我有条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.55,0:08:15.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,献上皇帝军拥有的所有圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣印是为了让唯一神复活而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是谁  独占它的人都得受到惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是皇帝也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.06,0:08:30.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧陛下绝非独占圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.24,0:08:35.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下的目的是利用圣印消除大陆全土的混沌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.20,0:08:40.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这根教团用唯一神的力量根绝大陆的混沌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.75,0:08:45.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界创造乐园的目的不是一样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝军的目的跟教团一样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.67,0:08:55.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,住ロ  敢用狂言迷惑教徒可饶不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…普莉希拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧涅大人  好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是普莉希拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧陛下总是公然宣称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果自己有那个力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就要终结混沌的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.92,0:09:29.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是让唯一神复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.84,0:09:33.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是神的代理  教皇猊下的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.67,0:09:37.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,绝非平民出身的小子能干的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在想让神明复活这一崇高行为前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,身份有关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在神明面前所有人应该都平等才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.56,0:09:51.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,约瑟夫阁下目前即将开展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.27,0:09:56.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,改日再让普莉希拉司教辩解您意下如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不会开战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为提欧大人无意战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人确实不是教团的信徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我父亲教租埃内斯托曾再三训诫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:14.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不可将信仰强加于人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家应该也听过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.55,0:10:21.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  教祖大人是这么说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  请回想教主的话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要唯一神复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们便能从混沌的痛苦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从纷争的悲伤中解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是死后的乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而是现实的乐园实现的那天将到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.46,0:11:00.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是圣杯的光芒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是圣杯吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.85,0:11:12.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人一定能终结混沌的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以会获得前往那位大人身边的天启
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了见证这一伟业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣女大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣女普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是慌的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去  恐怕那小丫头会被奉为教团领导着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我究竟该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,主人一旦力竭 圣印便会转变为混沌核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让信徒们亲眼见证圣杯转变为混沌的场面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.56,0:11:54.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该宣誓过忠于向潘多拉理念的人履行使命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:11:58.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子我误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧皇帝欲将圣印据为己有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而普莉希拉司教是帮凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.67,0:12:21.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我轻信了约瑟夫司教这番话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…猊下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.72,0:12:27.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我雷欧涅由衷向您致歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会接受与皇帝军议和的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢  猊下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还望您今后接过提欧皇帝的圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让唯一神复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这是我该做的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:15.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把那异教徒抓起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.94,0:13:26.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我以教皇之名宣布普莉希拉司教是异教徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我询问唯一神该如何审判她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.28,0:13:33.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后获得了赐死的天启
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我  西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了我们的目的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这时候杀死教皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,开战就不可避免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是变成那样  普莉希拉所做的一切就白费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这圣杯是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.57,0:14:10.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  想必很快就会破碎并转变为混沌核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这不废话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.33,0:14:16.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,主人一死圣印当然会破碎并转变为混沌核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.38,0:14:28.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助了普莉希拉司教的你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必会前往地狱永远痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.53,0:14:54.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说支持普莉希拉是罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我很乐意坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.25,0:15:03.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  最好别以为能轻易要我们的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣印教团的信徒们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们究竟看见了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.10,0:15:17.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉说过  信仰在心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.85,0:15:22.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣女普莉希拉才是真正的圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毁坏她的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虚假的圣杯 教皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.53,0:15:33.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣战士们  立刻制裁他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.96,0:15:42.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这不应该…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉的圣印…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没变成混沌核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是真正的圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不变成混沌核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说她是…真正的圣女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说她不是真的圣女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那你把那圣印夺走便是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能成为真正的圣杯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.89,0:16:46.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,光是杀害圣女就已经是罪孽深重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还要做这么可怕的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我办不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你想背叛潘多拉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,随你处置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总比坠入地狱强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能让你杀了重要的证人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不用追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算杀了他也于事无补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,言归正传  把提欧大人叫来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.31,0:17:28.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.16,0:17:39.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,事情的经过看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正如普莉希拉所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.49,0:17:46.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝必定会让唯一神复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是她该做的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言  西露卡大人嘱咐过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.94,0:18:11.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要您尽快前往教团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也随行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.24,0:18:16.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:23.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拼上性命保护好皇帝陛下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.79,0:18:28.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能别说什么拼上性命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再让任何一人先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没那么容易死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然避免了与教皇军开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.31,0:18:49.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过与魔法师协会的战斗还在前方等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必会有很多人丧命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过唯独你绝对不能死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我早有觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说实话  现在感觉我的心快屈服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉等于是被我杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我明知有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,却把她送到了教皇身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是只有那个女孩才能办到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.84,0:19:21.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你有只有你才能办到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.19,0:19:38.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会继承你的圣杯和理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.32,0:19:47.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓  定会终结混沌的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说这就是我该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣杯就交给我保管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.12,0:20:28.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请终结混沌的时代  提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.54,0:20:34.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  请创造岀能让人们安心生活的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.59,0:20:47.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝提欧•科尔内罗已成为圣杯的守护者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,信仰唯一神的人们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请崇拜皇帝  成为他的人民吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是教皇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.78,0:21:10.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正因杀死了真正的圣女而害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.12,0:21:15.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了调查魔法师协会和教团的关系将他抓了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该如何处置呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给你处置了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  只要看见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道自己会因愤怒做出什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.23,0:21:35.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.67,0:08:50.00,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,不是因为害怕触怒神明才说谎吗
